body:
Name some funny things your team said or some achievements/accomplishments you or the team had while playing in the Race to Victory tournament

My Quotes:
"If we get a touch against PPB on the first match, Sem has to talk"
Last 5 seconds of the match: 
"(color) wool has been touched"
Still waiting for sem to talk :c


Good luck to Bad Company and PPB for the final and Good luck to Fortissimus and Apollo for Bronze Final!
